data.description: Updated and well-kept 3 BR 2 BA home with great space for entertaining and relaxing. Galley kitchen with granite countertops and newer appliances flanked by open utility/pantry area and large comfortable dining/hearth room. Covered patio with dining area, food prep, and storage with bar top seating. Inground vinyl pool with new liner. Master has two closets with en-suite updated bathroom with rain showerhead and exterior access. Updated hall bath with tin ceiling, contemporary sink and walk-in shower with rainhead. Backyard Storage shed conveys.
